Date: Fri, 22 May 2026 22:38:36 +1200
Subject: [PATCH 07/27] feat: add boot.md builtin hook for startup prompt
 execution

Reads ~/.hermes/BOOT.md on gateway startup and runs it as an agent
prompt in a background thread (daemon=True) so it never blocks startup.
Adapted from the old fork to use hermes_cli.config.get_hermes_home().

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>
